214.question: What is the results of multimodal compared to unimodal models?
214.response: {'Answer': 'Multimodal models show improved performance over unimodal models in terms of precision, recall, and accuracy. This is evident from the Precision vs Recall and ROC curve plots which show that models with multimodal inputs (FCM-ALL, TKM-All, SCM-All) generally outperform the unimodal model (FCM-I) and the baseline LSTM model that uses only text.
